ional samples. The fact that 'post-starburst' signatures can be\nattained via various evolutionary channels explains the diversity of observed\nproperties, and lends support to the idea that slower quenching channels are\nimportant at low redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2019 17:54:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
