the drastic spectral transformations seen in this\nAGN. Although the peak luminosity and timescales are consistent with those of\ntidal disruption events seen in inactive galaxies, the spectral properties are\nnot. The X-ray emission displays a markedly different behavior, with frequent\nflares on timescales of hours to days, and will be presented in a companion\npublication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2019 18:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 15:53:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
