 and the\nstraightforward suppression of noise usually associated with squeezed light.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Mar 2019 08:11:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 06:32:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 04:07:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-17"}
