ction and the\ndeformation potentials. We perform photoluminescence excitation measurements to\ndemonstrate that the excitation of the emitters is most efficient by LO-phonon\nassisted absorption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Mar 2019 08:53:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-15"}
